{"questionId":"31769448","questionHtml":"<p>Show that the sprinkler rotates through an angle of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><mn>8</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;radians in one second.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>EITHER</strong></p>\n<p>the sprinkler rotates through (an angle of) <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi></math> (radians) every <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>16</mn></math> seconds and hence rotates through <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi></mrow><mn>16</mn></mfrac></math> (radians) in <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn></math> second&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><em>A1</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong>OR</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi></mrow><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>16</mn><mo>⇒</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo></mrow></mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi></mrow><mn>16</mn></mfrac><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><mn>8</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><em>A1</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong>THEN</strong></p>\n<p>sprinkler rotates through an angle of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><mn>8</mn></mfrac></math> radians in one second&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><em>AG</em></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><strong><em>[1 mark]</em></strong></p>","meta":{"questionId":"31769448","referenceCode":"24M.2.SL.TZ2.9b","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Show that the sprinkler rotates through an angle of π8 radians in one second.","paper":"2","level":"SL","questionNumber":"b","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 3— Geometry and trigonometry","Topic 3— Geometry and trigonometry","SL 3.4—Circle: radians, arcs, sectors"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}